  "Description": {
    "English": "A living, fertile egg, <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">ready to hatch!</span><br><br>The biomechanical creature inside is silent, waiting to be hatched from stasis.<br><br>Scans indicate the being within will grow into a <span class=\"name name-stellar\">dutiful</span> companion, motivated to assist in exploration.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一枚有生命的、可孵化的卵，<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">已经准备好孵化！</span><br><br>里面的生物力学生物正静静等待着从休眠中孵化出来。<br><br>根据扫描结果显示，这个生物会成长为<span class=\"name name-stellar\">尽职</span>的同伴，能够在探索中积极提供协助。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "有生命、可孵化的蛋，<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">且即將孵化！</span><br><br>裡面的生物力學有機體沉默著，等待從休眠狀態中孵化而出。<br><br>掃描結果顯示，內部生物將成長為<span class=\"name name-stellar\">責任心重</span>同伴，會積極協助探索。"
